snippet.title: Jeff The Killer: Slendermans Betrayal
snippet.description:

Android Download: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PoisonGames.JeffTheKillerSlendermansBetrayal
PC Download: https://gamejolt.com/games/JeffTheKillerSlendermansBetrayal/615498

After a long time, you decided to come back to your hometown!
But things are different. Old threat, Slenderman is here. His plan is to destroy you
once and for all. He took and killed all your victims and he is after you now.
Look out, he is not alone!
His sidekicks are helping him along the way. 
You need to find his hideout. There will be a lot of different tasks you need
to complete, before you can find and fight this menace!
